book.synopsis: When Shawna Lee Quinn, a rival bakery owner, is found shot to death in the back of the Magnolia Blossom Bakery, Hannah Swenson becomes the prime suspect in the crime, and with a little help from her friends, sets out to serve up the real killer. Reprint.
